**** Installing Flask ****
pip3 install Flask
apt-get install python3-flask

**** Running the application ***
1. Requirements must be installed in the environment - pip3 install -r requirements.txt
2. Following this tutorial - https://flask.palletsprojects.com/en/1.1.x/tutorial/factory/
Run next commands in console in the project path ./fbp-vs-oop/
    $ export FLASK_APP=flaskr
    $ export FLASK_ENV=development
    $ flask init-db
    $ flask run
3. Run the main file of the fbp-vs-oop project passing "soa_app_min" as a parameter